    {
        "content": "<p>Šeit punktiem <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/13615005029\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/13615005029</a> / <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/5120414433\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/5120414433</a> adrese pielikta Blaumaņa iela 38/40, bet ēkai <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/161411202\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/161411202</a> adrese ir Pērses iela 9/11. Vai te kaut kas ar izvietojumu b0tu mulsina vai arī datos kaut kas šķībs? <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/Z11EEI4F6AGpi0usfCfM_AVG/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/Z11EEI4F6AGpi0usfCfM_AVG/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1291x994\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/Z11EEI4F6AGpi0usfCfM_AVG/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/13615005029\" style='background-image: url(\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67\")'></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/13615005029\" title=\"Node: ‪Ilze Pilsētniece‬ (‪13615005029‬)\">Node: ‪Ilze Pilsētniece‬ (‪13615005029‬)</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/5120414433\" style='background-image: url(\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a